        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你……想做什么？"
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "把我检查过的记忆隔开，或者说暂时剥离出去。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "芙提雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "！！"
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果说我们是在大海捞针，那就把水放干，让那根“针”无处可逃。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，不行。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "果然，瑟瑞斯的拒绝十分坚决。她是脑科学学者，我已经预料到她不会同意这个计划。"
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟瑞斯",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，记忆并不像黄油那样，可以随意切开又组合回去。"
